'''Taylor Thomas Lindsey''' (born December 2, 1991) is a [[professional baseball]] player in the [[Los Angeles Angels of Anaheim]] organization. He is the 93rd prospect by Baseball America.<ref>http://www.baseballamerica.com/minors/2014-baseball-america-top-100-prospects-free/</ref>

Lindsey was drafted 37th overall by the [[Los Angeles Angels of Anaheim]] in the [[2010 Major League Baseball Draft]], out of [[Desert Mountain High School]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100607&content_id=10927950&vkey=news_ana&fext=.jsp&c_id=ana |title=Angels pick two in supplemental round &#124; angels.com: News |publisher=Mlb.mlb.com |date= |accessdate=December 12, 2013}}</ref>

